review:
if you think this will be ahealla cute game, you will learn that you where dead wrong as that thought crossed your mind.

i don't know what to say, sure the sheep are pretty cute and their sounds are even more cute but the death of your sheep, if you can't keep them alive will be literally heartbreaking ;v;

even i love sheep and don't wanna see them dead it's a great game and i don't regret that i bought it :3
